data.text: 0 g sugar. 0 g net carbs. This product is Keto certified. ketocertified.com. Not a low calorie food. See nutrition facts panel for calorie information. Non GMO Project verified. nongmoproject.org. Made with grass-fed butter + MCT oil. Grass-fed butter + protein. MCT oil brain boost. Super versatile. Hello, sunshine. What is MCT oil? MCT = Medium Chain Triglycerides. It is a special type of fat found in coconut oil that is really easy for your body to digest. After consumption, MCTs are quickly converted into ketones, which are a primarily fuel source for your brain and muscles. Grass-Fed Butter is Best: Grass-fed butter is high in omega-3 fatty acids, vitamins A, D, E and K and is much lower in lactose than pasteurized milk. Our grass-fed butter from pasture-raised cows has a creamy, luxe texture and can make you feel fuller longer. Picknik's Creamer is Super Versatile: Picnik Creamer is like half-and-half's sexier, healthier, smarter cousin! Coffee is our creamer's best friend, but also great in smoothies, and is a perfect replacement for milk anytime you're baking or cooking. Your rule! I have a deep love for the benefits of grass-fed butter and MCT oil. These superstar ingredients keep me feeling full, alert and like I'm living my best life. Our Keto Creamer allows you to experience the magic for yourself! It's as easy as pouring a splash into your coffee or smoothie. At Picnik, we pride ourselves on creating products that make you feel and function your very best. We believe in supporting your health and lifestyle, no matter what your dietary point of view. Next time you are in Austin, come visit one of our cafes. We'd love to host y'all. Here's to a radiant life! - Naomi. Founder, Picnik. picnikshop.com. Facebook; Instagram. (at)picnikshop.
